#

Savory Minced Pork Lettuce Wraps

$15.99
320 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbHigh-Protein

Tags:

Asian-inspiredHealthyQuick meal

Description

Delicious, low-carb wraps filled with seasoned minced pork and fresh veggies.

Ingredients

  • Minced pork: 500g
  • Lettuce leaves (butter or romaine): 8-10 leaves
  • Garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • Ginger (grated): 1 inch
  • Soy sauce (low sodium): 2 tbsp
  • Hoisin sauce: 1 tbsp
  • Green onions (sliced): 2
  • Red bell pepper (diced): 1
  • Carrots (grated): 1
  • Sesame oil: 1 tsp
  • Salt and pepper: to taste
